General.Name: Belararox Ltd
General.Description: Belararox Limited engages in the exploration and development of mineral resource projects in Australia. The company explores for zinc, copper, gold, silver, nickel, and lead deposits. It holds 100% interests in the Belara project that covers an area of 643 square kilometers located in New South Wales; and Bullabulling project that consists of 26 exploration licences and covers an area of 49 square kilometers located in Coolgardie, Western Australia. The company was incorporated in 2021 and is based in Perth, Australia.
